And this is Colossians beginning in chapter four, verse two, continuing earnestly in prayer, being vigilant in it with Thanksgiving.

00:15.447 --> 00:30.482
Meanwhile praying also for us that God would open to us a door for the word to speak the mystery of Christ for which I am also in chains, that I may make and manifest as I ought to speak.

