love without truth weakens and is soft truth without love becomes harshness and love without truth becomes compromise enabling even a safe church does not celebrate sin oh it's okay go ahead and sin God's got more grace and just keep doing what you're doing you know God will forgive you that's not what we do but we also don't browbeat

18:33.090 --> 18:35.433
and crush those who are sitting.

