18:56.835 --> 19:00.640
We don't demand and crush and beat people over it and weaponize.

19:00.660 --> 19:01.781
Say, you got to be holy tonight.

19:01.861 --> 19:02.962
I don't know why you're here.

19:04.642 --> 19:06.785
