19:07.065 --> 19:08.627
I've heard that before in other churches.

19:09.468 --> 19:19.241
Listen, folks need to learn some way and we're to disciple people in the way of Christ, not expect people who've never known to know.

19:21.163 --> 19:23.606
And that's one of the things we learn, isn't it?

19:24.748 --> 19:26.430
